metadata.name: Sick Ape Society
metadata.description: Sick Ape Society is a secret community of Sick Apes that live in the ERC721A metaverse jungle. They stick together and try to survive in the era of scams and rug pulls that spoil their environment. Sick Ape Society is a project with great utilities and long-term ambitions. We combined the best aspects of different NFT projects and created the product that gives a lot of benefits.
